	<tr>
		<td style="font-family: Trebuchet MS; font-size: 8pt; color: #FFFFFF; font-weight: bold; text-align: left; background-color: #333333; border-left: 2px solid #000000; border-right: 2px solid #FFFFFF; border-top: 2px solid #000000; border-bottom: 2px solid #FFFFFF">
          		<br><u><i><font color="#FFFF00">MISC CODES:</font></i></u><br>
			&nbsp; While in the game, press select to get to the inventory screen. Highlight the timex and enter the codes - Get Every Item for the Current Level -
                  &nbsp; <font color="#00FF00">Hold Down+R1+R2+L1+L2, and press triangle</font>&nbsp;
			<br>&nbsp; While in the game, press select to get to the inventory screen. Highlight the timex and enter the codes - Unlimited Health, Ammo, and Weapons -
                  &nbsp; <font color="#00FF00">Hold Up+R1+R2+L1+L2, and press triangle</font>&nbsp;
			<br>&nbsp; Unlimited ammo Unlimited medikits and ammo - At the inventory screen highlight a small medikit and press -
                  &nbsp; <font color="#00FF00">L1 + L2 + R1 + R2 + Up and press Square</font>&nbsp;<br><br>
	 </tr>
